{"tid":2395883,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"教育部發預警：提醒中國留學生謹慎選擇赴澳洲學習","createTime":"2021-02-05T07:43:14.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-05T08:47:03.000Z","uid":230530,"like":12,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"2c254133299aea3fd0f13dd0e58aadc7b828fcab","tid":2395883,"uid":230530,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-05T07:43:14.000Z","msg":"中國同澳洲關係繼續陷於低潮，教育部發布今年第1號留學預警，指近期澳洲多地連續發生中國留學生遇襲的惡性事件，對留學人員的人身安全造成嚴重威脅，指當前全球新冠肺炎疫情形勢依然十分嚴峻，國際旅行仍存在較大風險，提醒留學生，充分做好安全風險評估，謹慎選擇前往或返回澳洲學習。 <br />\n<br />\n原文網址：<a href=\"https://www.881903.com/news/china/2377984\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.881903.com%2Fnews%2Fchina%2F2377984&d=GtJgxCFvwMhqeg%2B2Fxb9EegAExyYYV7WT87CuOwwBqU%3D&h=ac9f878e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.881903.com/news/china/2377984</a><br />\n<br />\n楊潤雄譚罐宗<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/02.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/02.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ce272c96c9cde91aa3914d8aaa88a3f5f1aa6d14","tid":2395883,"uid":55913,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-05T08:20:01.000Z","msg":"人大攪移民公司<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />通蕃賣國！<br />\n一定要捉拿歸案"},{"pid":"78b406e4ec56addacb20887203b8ca795010bbf1","tid":2395883,"uid":53026,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-05T08:31:38.000Z","msg":"預警你老母，警告就警告啦，凡警告都係事發前發出架啦，使撚預"},{"pid":"35603a54b1e571e39c026ac5cb36072f46c9f76a","tid":2395883,"uid":73350,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-05T08:35:16.000Z","msg":"海外讀書風險：<br />\n澳洲&mdash; 驅逐出境 <br />\n中國&mdash; 死於非命"},{"pid":"da0cde76133a059d0af24b047b38039e2f9d0ac4","tid":2395883,"uid":152476,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-05T08:37:12.000Z","msg":"中國人去乜野澳洲讀書<br />\n國家無好學校？<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hate.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"160ddfadef689482a4b3f4a835772e56f8ae792e","tid":2395883,"uid":53026,"like":0,"disli